                     <interp inst="t18280911-314-person1704" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was standing at the top of White Conduit-street, and saw the prisoner running with a number of persons after him; he threw down these trousers, ran about twenty yards further, and was taken by Whitmore.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280911-314-person1705">
